General.Name: Golos
General.Description: Социальная сеть на основе блокчейна для русскоязычных людей. Это спин-офф из системы Steemit. Steem владеет 10% GOLOS.

ICO.Description:
1000 BTC was raised with the largest investor contributing 3.5%. ICO transactions.

  • 70% of the development and application protocol
  • 10% payment license Inc. stim. in accordance with the agreement litsenzinnym
  • 10% of the founders of the team fee
  • 10% compensation cyber Fund for the financing of start-up

Bonus Structure:

  • 25% in the first 15 days
  • 20% from 16 days to 18 days
  • 15% from 19 days to 21 days
  • 10% from 22 days to 24 days
  • 5% from 25 days to 27 days
  • 0% from 28 days to 30 days

Token reserve split

10% to cyber team, 10% to initial participants, 10% for development, 10% for team
